This paper deals with a sequential subset selection problem under parameter uncertainty, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper proposes an approach to adapt Thompson Sampling to this problem, which is a popular algorithm in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
